Global setup:

 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email jm60697@gmail.com
        
Next steps:

  mkdir catss
  cd catss
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:kyber/catss.git
  git push origin master
      
Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:kyber/catss.git
  git push origin master
      
